<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>刀空手游装备回收价格表</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a1a 0%, #121a30 100%);
            font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 200 200"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="rgba(10,10,20,0.8)"/><path d="M0,100 Q50,150 100,100 T200,100" stroke="rgba(212,175,55,0.05)" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/></svg>');
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .container {
            position: relative;
            width: 900px;
            max-width: 100%;
            padding: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0c0c1d, #1a1a2e);
            border: 4px solid;
            border-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #d4af37, #b8860b, #d4af37) 1;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.6);
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        /* 装饰元素 */
        .corner-decoration {
            position: absolute;
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            top: -5px;
            right: -5px;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path d="M100,0 L100,100 L0,100 Z" fill="rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2)"/></svg>') no-repeat;
            background-size: contain;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 10%;
            width: 80%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d4af37, transparent);
        }
        
        .title {
            font-size: 46px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f9d71c, #d4af37);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(249, 215, 28, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #b8860b, #d4af37);
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            margin: 0 5px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.7); }
            70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 12px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0); }
            100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(212, 175, 55, 0); }
        }
        
        .requirements {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border: 2px solid #d4af37;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .requirements h3 {
            color: #f9d71c;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(249, 215, 28, 0.5);
        }
        
        .requirements p {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .requirements .important {
            color: #ff5555;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 85, 85, 0.5);
        }
        
        .price-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 30px 0;
            background: rgba(10, 10, 20, 0.7);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .price-table th {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #2a1a3e, #1a1a3e);
            color: #f9d71c;
            padding: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #d4af37;
        }
        
        .price-table td {
            padding: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
        }
        
        .price-table tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: rgba(30, 30, 50, 0.4);
        }
        
        .price-table tr:hover {
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
            transform: scale(1.02);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .reincarnation {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d4af37;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .sword-icon {
            font-size: 26px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #f9d71c;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(249, 215, 28, 0.5);
        }
        
        .price {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #4caf50;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.5);
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
        }
        
        .qr-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .qr-code {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 5px solid #d4af37;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .qr-code::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1), rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3));
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .qr-code div {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .download-info {
            text-align: left;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            max-width: 350px;
        }
        
        .download-info h3 {
            color: #f9d71c;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(249, 215, 28, 0.5);
        }
        
        .download-info p {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        
        .download-info p i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #d4af37;
            font-size: 22px;
            min-width: 22px;
        }
        
        .note {
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
            border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
        }
        
        .note p {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .explosion {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            font-size: 50px;
            animation: explode 1.5s infinite;
            color: #ffcc00;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.8);
            z-index: 10;
        }
        
        @keyframes explode {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.7; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.3); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.7; }
        }
        
        .limited-tag {
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-5deg);
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff0000, #ff5252);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);
            z-index: 10;
            animation: shake 2s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes shake {
            0% { transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-5deg); }
            50% { transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(5deg); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-5deg); }
        }
        
        .fan-group {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff6b6b, #ff8e8e);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 6px 15px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 22px;
            animation: pulse-red 1.5s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse-red {
            0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.7); }
            70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0); }
            100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 107, 107, 0); }
        }
        
        .countdown {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .countdown-item {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            border: 2px solid #d4af37;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            min-width: 70px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .countdown-value {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f9d71c;
        }
        
        .countdown-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }
        
        .floating-swords {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .sword {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 30px;
            color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
            animation: float 15s infinite linear;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0; }
            10% { opacity: 0.5; }
            90% { opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { transform: translateY(-100vh) rotate(360deg); opacity: 0; }
        }
        
        .hot-tag {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: -10px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff5252, #ff0000);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
            z-index: 10;
        }
        
        /* 照片展示区域 */
        .game-showcase {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .screenshots {
            flex: 1;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            height: 250px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 2px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
        }
        
        .screenshots img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }
        
        .screenshots:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        .screenshot-label {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            color: #d4af37;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .carousel {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 3px solid #d4af37;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
        }
        
        .carousel-inner {
            display: flex;
            height: 100%;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }
        
        .carousel-item {
            min-width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        
        .carousel-caption {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 22px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #000;
        }
        
        .carousel-control {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            color: #d4af37;
            border: none;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 10;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .carousel-control:hover {
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.8);
            color: #000;
        }
        
        .carousel-prev {
            left: 15px;
        }
        
        .carousel-next {
            right: 15px;
        }
        
        .carousel-indicators {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .carousel-indicator {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .carousel-indicator.active {
            background: #d4af37;
            transform: scale(1.3);
        }
        
        .photo-wall {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .photo-item {
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            border: 2px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
        }
        
        .photo-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        
        .photo-item:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        
        .photo-caption {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            color: #d4af37;
            padding: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .photo-section-title {
            text-align: center;
            color: #d4af37;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin: 25px 0 15px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .photo-section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -8px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 100px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d4af37, transparent);
        }

        /* 游戏下载区域样式 */
        .download-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
        }

        .download-title {
            color: #f9d71c;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(249, 215, 28, 0.5);
        }

        .download-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .download-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-width: 200px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .download-btn i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .download-btn.android {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #3ddc84, #2bb673);
        }

        .download-btn.ios {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #007aff, #0040ff);
        }

        .download-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        .download-btn:active {
            transform: translateY(1px);
        }

        .download-tip {
            color: #d4af37;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* 响应式调整 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            .title {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
            
            .subtitle {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            .qr-section {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .price-table th, .price-table td {
                padding: 12px;
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            .download-info {
                max-width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .download-info p {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .game-showcase {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .carousel {
                height: 200px;
            }
            
            .photo-wall {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }

            .download-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .download-btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 250px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="floating-swords" id="sword-container"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="corner-decoration"></div>
        <div class="explosion">💥</div>
        <div class="limited-tag">新区限时特惠</div>
        
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="title">刀空手游装备回收价格表</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">新区开服 <span class="highlight">1~3天</span> · 游戏内<span class="highlight">爆率超高</span></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 游戏宣传轮播图 -->
        <div class="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <!-- 替换以下3个轮播图URL -->
                <div class="carousel-item" style="background-image: url('https://i.postimg.cc/gkYcV7RX/20250613195021-19.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80')">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">顶级装备展示 - 30转神装</div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item" style="background-image: url('https://i.postimg.cc/pLS2tXSz/20250613195025-20.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80')">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">新区开服盛况 - 万人同屏</div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item" style="background-image: url('https://i.postimg.cc/8cwSX1WF/20250613195028-21.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80')">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">世界BOSS战 - 高爆率装备</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control carousel-prev">❮</button>
            <button class="carousel-control carousel-next">❯</button>
            <div class="carousel-indicators">
                <div class="carousel-indicator active"></div>
                <div class="carousel-indicator"></div>
                <div class="carousel-indicator"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="requirements">
            <h3>★ 必读提示 ★</h3>
            <p>仅限开服1-3天新区 · 超高爆率 · 真实回收</p>
            <p class="important">关注主播进粉丝群报备领取打金资格</p>
            <div class="fan-group">进粉丝群领取专属资格和打金福利</div>
            
            <div class="countdown">
                <div class="countdown-item">
                    <div class="countdown-value" id="days">03</div>
                    <div class="countdown-label">天</div>
                </div>
                <div class="countdown-item">
                    <div class="countdown-value" id="hours">12</div>
                    <div class="countdown-label">时</div>
                </div>
                <div class="countdown-item">
                    <div class="countdown-value" id="minutes">45</div>
                    <div class="countdown-label">分</div>
                </div>
                <div class="countdown-item">
                    <div class="countdown-value" id="seconds">30</div>
                    <div class="countdown-label">秒</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 游戏装备展示区 -->
        <div class="game-showcase">
            <div class="screenshots">
                <!-- 替换装备展示图片1 -->
                <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/MGhK1Kbq/20250613195000-15.png?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="15转装备">
                <div class="screenshot-label">15转双属性神装</div>
            </div>
